Wait, I removed `.use-grid` from the main CSS but there are still responsive rules referencing it:
```css
@media (max-width: 980px) {
  .retro-layout .use-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .retro-layout .use-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
```

I need to update those to reference `.caps-grid` instead. Let me find and update them.

